nodes.id: 中国国民党革命委员会中央委员会

description.zh-cn: 中国国民党革命委员会的中央领导机构。
description.en: The central leading body of the Revolutionary Committee of the Chinese Kuomintang.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国政治术语，指在中国大陆范围内，除执政党中国共产党以外的、被中华人民共和国政府承认拥有参政议政权力的8个政党的统称。
description.en: A political term in the People's Republic of China, referring to the eight legally recognized political parties, other than the ruling Communist Party of China, that have the right to participate in and deliberate on state affairs.
